{"id":564496337,"lang":"java","time":"4 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1633183489,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"10 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/564496337/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"45.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int romanToInt(String s) {\n        int num = 0;\n        int i = 0;\n        Map<String, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();\n        map.put(\"M\", 1000);\n        map.put(\"C\", 100);\n        map.put(\"D\", 500);\n        map.put(\"I\", 1);\n        map.put(\"V\", 5);\n        map.put(\"L\", 50);\n        map.put(\"X\", 10);\n        \n        while(i < s.length()){\n            String cur = s.substring(i, i+1);\n            int curVal = map.get(cur);\n            int nextVal = 0;\n            if(i+1 < s.length()){\n                String next = s.substring(i+1, i+2);\n                nextVal = map.get(next);\n            }\n            if(curVal < nextVal){\n                num += (nextVal - curVal);\n                i += 2;\n            } else {\n                num += curVal;\n                i++;\n            }\n        }\n        return num;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer"}
